  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Les Grangettes is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner. <strong>There is no afternoon tea or wine with dinner.  Evening meals are served seven nights a </strong><strong>week.</strong></p>
<p>Start your day at the buffet breakfast which includes a classic continental offering, as well as additional hot options.</p>
<p>A tasty three course meal with a choice of menu is served for dinner. The menu includes a variety of local and international dishes. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
