  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>The 28 bedrooms are all on the first floor and are simply but comfortably furnished to provide excellent value accommodation. </p>
<p><strong>Twin or Double Rooms</strong> can sleep two people with twin or double beds, please specify your preference at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Family Quad Rooms</strong> can sleep up to four people and have a double bed and bunk beds.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> sleep one person in a single bed and have a view of the courtyard. These rooms are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p>Please note that rooms 11 to 19 are above Jack's Bar and can be affected by noise.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Resort and/or mountain views</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Toiletries </li>
<li>En-suite bathroom with a bath (room 12 has a wet room)</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
